<dec f='include/pulse/mainloop.h' l='109' type='int pa_mainloop_iterate(pa_mainloop * m, int block, int * retval)'/>
<doc f='include/pulse/mainloop.h' l='103'>/** Run a single iteration of the main loop. This is a convenience function
for pa_mainloop_prepare(), pa_mainloop_poll() and pa_mainloop_dispatch().
Returns a negative value on error or exit request. If block is nonzero,
block for events if none are queued. Optionally return the return value as
specified with the main loop&apos;s quit() routine in the integer variable retval points
to. On success returns the number of sources dispatched in this iteration. */</doc>
